00:27:24.870 --> 00:27:25.791
Right now, he's fine.

00:27:25.813 --> 00:27:27.630
But Zhou Muyan
didn't care for his well-being.

00:27:27.630 --> 00:27:28.540
He even said something like that.

00:27:28.540 --> 00:27:29.540
It'd caused widespread outrage.

00:27:29.540 --> 00:27:31.430
Oh my goodness! He went overboard.

00:27:31.430 --> 00:27:32.470
Who can tolerate that?

00:27:32.470 --> 00:27:34.670
That's typical Zhou Muyan, you know?

00:27:35.191 --> 00:27:37.102
Sky Fire is at the top
of the trending topics.

00:27:37.390 --> 00:27:39.230
"Sky Fire corporate culture."

00:27:39.540 --> 00:27:41.540
"Employees have no dignity."

00:27:41.780 --> 00:27:43.780
"Undergraduates, do not join Sky Fire."

00:27:46.020 --> 00:27:47.500
"Sky Fire, just close down."

00:27:49.260 --> 00:27:50.020
Wei,

00:27:50.020 --> 00:27:51.500
you've finally gotten your revenge.

00:27:52.230 --> 00:27:53.300
What are you talking about?

00:27:53.300 --> 00:27:54.340
We're just employees.

00:27:54.340 --> 00:27:55.580
All these grudges don't matter.

00:27:55.990 --> 00:27:56.710
Yeah.

00:27:56.710 --> 00:27:59.020
But even employees like us
have our own dignity!

00:27:59.100 --> 00:28:00.300
Precisely.

00:28:02.230 --> 00:28:04.230
I've actually worked at
several companies before

00:28:04.230 --> 00:28:05.710
where workplace bullying occurred.

00:28:05.710 --> 00:28:07.540
This issue
should've been addressed long ago.

00:28:07.540 --> 00:28:09.746
A terrible company like Sky Fire
will be exposed eventually.

00:28:10.020 --> 00:28:11.300
It feels like

00:28:11.300 --> 00:28:13.630
a storm is brewing.

00:28:20.540 --> 00:28:22.300
They're too much.

00:28:23.820 --> 00:28:24.710
What's going on?

00:28:24.710 --> 00:28:26.300
This is ridiculous.

00:28:29.100 --> 00:28:31.300
Don't you think their boss is too shady?

00:28:32.191 --> 00:28:33.190
How could this happen?

00:28:33.190 --> 00:28:34.190
Yeah. What's going on?

00:28:34.340 --> 00:28:36.580
Who posted this video?

00:28:36.950 --> 00:28:37.780
Does he know

00:28:37.780 --> 00:28:38.580
how much money

00:28:38.580 --> 00:28:40.100
the company and I have lost

00:28:40.100 --> 00:28:42.100
because of his actions?

00:28:42.100 --> 00:28:43.540
He must've lost his mind!

00:28:44.260 --> 00:28:45.990
Find him

00:28:45.990 --> 00:28:47.710
by hook or by crook!

00:28:47.710 --> 00:28:48.820
I'm going to sue him

00:28:48.820 --> 00:28:50.300
until he goes bankrupt!

00:28:51.710 --> 00:28:53.630
What's with all
the secret filming these days?

00:28:55.568 --> 00:28:57.020
Why are you still standing there?

00:28:58.580 --> 00:29:00.580
Do you think it's funny too?

00:29:01.870 --> 00:29:03.060
Listen up!

00:29:03.060 --> 00:29:04.780
Find him

00:29:04.780 --> 00:29:06.580
at all costs!

00:29:06.580 --> 00:29:07.780
Get lost!

00:29:07.990 --> 00:29:09.950
Get lost if you can't find him!

00:29:15.810 --> 00:29:17.790
What's with the horrible filming angle?

00:29:17.790 --> 00:29:18.400
Darn it!

00:29:24.580 --> 00:29:25.702
(Sky Fire, the Pit of Hell)
(Did you guys watch)

00:29:25.702 --> 00:29:26.390
(Talk, and You'll Lose Your Job)
(the video?)

00:29:26.390 --> 00:29:27.710
(That was insane.)

00:29:29.020 --> 00:29:29.950
(Listen,)

00:29:29.950 --> 00:29:31.630
(now that the HQ
has received news of this,)

00:29:31.630 --> 00:29:33.150
(they'll surely do something about it.)

00:29:34.435 --> 00:29:36.235
(I will finally have my revenge)

00:29:36.257 --> 00:29:38.100
(after working overtime for 45 days.)

00:29:40.020 --> 00:29:41.580
(We're finally going to be free.)

00:29:46.213 --> 00:29:47.630
All of you, stop what you're doing!

00:29:51.580 --> 00:29:52.780
Listen up.

00:29:53.300 --> 00:29:54.540
This is a warning.

00:29:54.780 --> 00:29:57.540
Do not post any detrimental remarks!

00:29:57.820 --> 00:29:58.870
Take your phone with you

00:29:59.020 --> 00:30:00.580
and come to my office in turn!

00:30:08.020 --> 00:30:09.060
Did you guys not hear me?

00:30:10.060 --> 00:30:11.340
Are you guys trying to rebel?

00:30:12.100 --> 00:30:13.300
Was it you?

00:30:14.100 --> 00:30:15.300
Was it you?

00:30:17.580 --> 00:30:18.540
You all...

00:30:19.100 --> 00:30:20.340
I'll definitely find out

00:30:20.340 --> 00:30:22.340
who posted the video!

00:30:22.710 --> 00:30:24.580
How dare you all rebel?

00:30:27.020 --> 00:30:27.780
Hello?

00:30:28.060 --> 00:30:29.470
Zhao, it's me.

00:30:30.580 --> 00:30:31.260
Meng Chang?

00:30:31.260 --> 00:30:32.670
Now that it has come to this,

00:30:32.857 --> 00:30:34.910
we have no choice
but to part ways with you guys.

00:30:34.910 --> 00:30:36.146
I hope Mr. Zhou can understand.

00:30:36.168 --> 00:30:37.020
What?

00:30:53.700 --> 00:30:57.980
(Fuhui)

00:30:59.020 --> 00:30:59.780
Mr. Li,

00:31:00.470 --> 00:31:02.540
the situation with
Sky Fire's Eternal Reincarnation

00:31:02.813 --> 00:31:04.500
has completely spiraled out of control.

00:31:04.990 --> 00:31:06.300
There's no room for salvation.

00:31:09.780 --> 00:31:11.540
Call Zhou Muyan.

00:31:15.300 --> 00:31:16.100
Mr. Zhou,

00:31:16.502 --> 00:31:18.924
Meng Chang and his company
have parted ways with us.

00:31:19.540 --> 00:31:20.710
As for the video,

00:31:20.880 --> 00:31:22.813
it's still at the top spot
for trending topics.

00:31:23.020 --> 00:31:24.390
The HQ said

00:31:24.390 --> 00:31:25.813
that they saw the video as well.

00:31:25.857 --> 00:31:27.780
Fuhui's stock price
also hit the lower limit today.

00:31:36.060 --> 00:31:36.820
Hello?

00:31:41.013 --> 00:31:41.870
May I help you, Sir?

00:31:43.390 --> 00:31:44.100
Understood.

00:31:48.230 --> 00:31:49.100
It's our boss.

00:31:52.780 --> 00:31:53.740
It's the chairman.

00:32:06.870 --> 00:32:07.780
Mr. Li,

00:32:09.020 --> 00:32:10.340
sorry for the shock.

00:32:10.340 --> 00:32:11.710
What the heck

00:32:11.710 --> 00:32:12.870
is Sky Fire doing?

00:32:12.870 --> 00:32:14.820
Is that how you develop video games?

00:32:14.820 --> 00:32:16.230
And, what's with the video?

00:32:16.230 --> 00:32:18.300
You've utterly embarrassed Fuhui.

00:32:18.300 --> 00:32:20.190
And, the consequences are devastating.

00:32:20.190 --> 00:32:22.235
Do you think there's no one
to keep you in check...

00:32:26.260 --> 00:32:26.990
That's

00:32:28.150 --> 00:32:28.990
my phone...

00:32:36.990 --> 00:32:38.060
(Fuhui)
(Lately,)

00:32:38.060 --> 00:32:40.780
(affairs related to
Sky Fire under Fuhui have attracted)

00:32:40.780 --> 00:32:42.500
(widespread public attention.)

00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:44.910
(We apologize for
the negative impact)

00:32:44.910 --> 00:32:46.820
(that it has brought upon society.)

00:32:47.100 --> 00:32:47.990
(In the future,)

00:32:47.990 --> 00:32:49.235
(Fuhui will place great importance)

00:32:49.257 --> 00:32:51.150
(on the physical and mental well-being
of our employees)

00:32:51.150 --> 00:32:52.829
(and conducts through self-reflection,)

00:32:52.830 --> 00:32:54.780
(and address the current
management's shortcomings.)

00:32:54.780 --> 00:32:55.580
(At the same time,)

00:32:55.580 --> 00:32:57.746
(we will embrace
innovation and authenticity.)

00:32:57.813 --> 00:32:59.190
(With authenticity as our core,)

00:32:59.190 --> 00:33:00.946
(Fuhui)
(with quality as our guiding principle,)

00:33:00.968 --> 00:33:03.280
(we shall foster a happy environment
where every employee is family.)

00:33:03.280 --> 00:33:04.629
(Announcement)
(Fuhui will continue to uphold)

00:33:04.630 --> 00:33:05.480
(our core principles)

00:33:05.740 --> 00:33:07.740
(and always be there for you all.)

00:33:07.740 --> 00:33:09.860
(Fuhui Group)

00:33:12.190 --> 00:33:13.020
Mr. Li Jr.

00:33:13.230 --> 00:33:13.990
Mr. Li Jr!

00:33:13.990 --> 00:33:14.390
It's fine.

00:33:14.390 --> 00:33:15.300
Mr. Li is in a bad mood.

00:33:15.300 --> 00:33:16.820
It won't take long.

00:33:16.820 --> 00:33:17.820
That's not it, Mr. Li Jr.

00:33:30.190 --> 00:33:30.780
Dad.

00:33:34.710 --> 00:33:35.780
I suppose

00:33:35.780 --> 00:33:38.050
Sky Fire has gotten the company
into deep trouble, right?

00:33:38.780 --> 00:33:39.540
It's like this.

00:33:40.300 --> 00:33:41.230
I have an idea.

00:33:41.230 --> 00:33:42.470
It'll definitely help you out.

00:33:45.390 --> 00:33:46.390
Tell me about it.

00:33:52.380 --> 00:33:54.020
(Tengda)

00:33:57.150 --> 00:33:59.100
Bao, I finished it in one minute.

00:33:59.100 --> 00:33:59.870
You lost.

00:33:59.870 --> 00:34:00.470
This...

00:34:00.470 --> 00:34:01.910
That doesn't count. I was lagging.

00:34:01.910 --> 00:34:02.870
Stop it.

00:34:02.870 --> 00:34:03.910
I found another new project.

00:34:03.910 --> 00:34:05.035
We must invest in it this time.

00:34:05.035 --> 00:34:07.150
Sometimes, Mr. Ma's preference
does leave me in awe.

00:34:07.630 --> 00:34:09.220
Please enlighten me.

00:34:09.220 --> 00:34:10.310
This is the plan.

00:34:12.990 --> 00:34:15.540
Ruan Guangjian's original artwork
is truly exceptional.

00:34:15.540 --> 00:34:16.990
We should learn from him.

00:34:16.990 --> 00:34:18.660
The color scheme is great as well.

00:34:21.100 --> 00:34:21.870
Ms. Xin.

00:34:23.324 --> 00:34:24.620
Have you watched the news?

00:34:24.620 --> 00:34:25.220
What happened?

00:34:25.220 --> 00:34:26.540
Fuhui and Sky Fire

00:34:26.540 --> 00:34:27.700
have parted ways.

00:34:29.430 --> 00:34:30.990
A new dawn is here.

00:34:30.990 --> 00:34:31.700
Son,

00:34:31.700 --> 00:34:32.990
I won't be picking you up today.

00:34:32.990 --> 00:34:34.310
Dad will pick you up.

00:34:34.946 --> 00:34:36.500
You haven't finished the previous batch

00:34:36.500 --> 00:34:37.470
Mr. Pei bought for you?

00:34:37.470 --> 00:34:39.470
Nope. He restocked it after that.

00:34:40.102 --> 00:34:40.750
Hi, Ms. Hailu.

00:34:40.750 --> 00:34:41.350
Ms. Hailu.

00:34:42.502 --> 00:34:43.500
Do you guys want some?

00:34:43.500 --> 00:34:44.670
We'll get reimbursed for it anyway.

00:34:44.670 --> 00:34:45.100
No thanks.

00:34:45.100 --> 00:34:47.180
Since he bought it for you,
you should keep it.

00:34:56.700 --> 00:34:57.350
Ms. Hailu.

00:34:57.950 --> 00:34:58.660
Ms. Hailu.

00:35:03.700 --> 00:35:06.700
(GM Office)

00:35:08.140 --> 00:35:09.060
Mr. Pei,

00:35:09.060 --> 00:35:10.350
Mr. Li Jr. is looking for you.

00:35:12.310 --> 00:35:14.100
Impossible!

00:35:14.180 --> 00:35:15.470
That's impossible!

00:35:16.835 --> 00:35:18.500
All of us know
the kind of person Li Shi is.

00:35:18.660 --> 00:35:20.350
Of course, he's up to no good.

00:35:20.368 --> 00:35:21.830
Now, he wants us to acquire Sky Fire?

00:35:21.830 --> 00:35:22.990
I won't agree to it!

00:35:23.146 --> 00:35:24.220
What a brilliant plan.

00:35:24.830 --> 00:35:26.013
So, Fuhui is trying to use

00:35:26.013 --> 00:35:27.835
Sky Fire's current failure
to their advantage

00:35:27.880 --> 00:35:29.660
and cast them away as a discarded pawn?

00:35:29.660 --> 00:35:30.220
That's right.

00:35:30.220 --> 00:35:32.220
You guys are overthinking it here.

00:35:32.220 --> 00:35:33.620
Everything'll work out

00:35:33.620 --> 00:35:34.830
as long as Mr. Pei is in charge.

00:35:34.830 --> 00:35:36.540
But if we acquire Sky Fire,

00:35:36.540 --> 00:35:38.430
does that mean Zhou Muyan
will join us as well?

00:35:38.435 --> 00:35:39.500
It doesn't matter who joins us

00:35:39.500 --> 00:35:41.302
as long as they don't
turn this into a rat race.

00:35:41.302 --> 00:35:42.257
I can't tolerate that.

00:35:42.390 --> 00:35:43.310
Lv, I agree with you.

00:35:43.310 --> 00:35:44.580
No one can tolerate them.

00:35:45.020 --> 00:35:47.540
Yang, we shouldn't
only challenge capitalism,

00:35:47.540 --> 00:35:48.990
we should also seek to understand it.

00:35:48.990 --> 00:35:50.470
I lack manpower.

00:35:50.470 --> 00:35:51.829
I'm busy rewriting the scripts.

00:35:51.830 --> 00:35:53.700
I don't have time to read
all those online novels.

00:35:53.700 --> 00:35:54.830
With this, I can hire more manpower

00:35:54.830 --> 00:35:56.120
to help me review the novels.

00:35:56.124 --> 00:35:57.540
I won't agree with this. No way.

00:35:58.020 --> 00:35:58.790
That's enough.

00:35:58.790 --> 00:35:59.700
Why get so agitated?

00:35:59.700 --> 00:36:00.620
Why disagree?

00:36:00.620 --> 00:36:01.524
Why recruit them?

00:36:01.546 --> 00:36:03.220
You can just post
a recruitment notice.

00:36:03.220 --> 00:36:03.700
No one...

00:36:03.700 --> 00:36:05.257
We're going to acquire
Sky Fire anyway.

00:36:08.830 --> 00:36:09.350
Mr. Li Jr.,

00:36:10.220 --> 00:36:11.413
Sky Fire has made

00:36:11.480 --> 00:36:13.580
significant contributions
to Fuhui after all.

00:36:13.580 --> 00:36:14.220
Don't you agree?

00:36:15.750 --> 00:36:17.430
But all gatherings must come to an end.

00:36:17.430 --> 00:36:19.350
Nothing lasts forever.

00:36:19.350 --> 00:36:19.990
Don't you agree?

00:36:19.990 --> 00:36:20.830
Mr. Li Jr.,

00:36:21.270 --> 00:36:23.100
what do you mean by that?

00:36:23.990 --> 00:36:24.750
Mr. Zhou,

00:36:25.080 --> 00:36:26.790
I'm just relaying Dad's message to you.

00:36:28.990 --> 00:36:29.700
But Mr. Zhou,

00:36:29.830 --> 00:36:31.580
I understand your feelings completely.

00:36:31.700 --> 00:36:33.140
After all, you guys have made

00:36:33.140 --> 00:36:34.568
significant contributions to Fuhui.

00:36:34.568 --> 00:36:36.500
And, there's another path you can take.

00:36:38.940 --> 00:36:42.900
(Sky Fire)

00:36:47.100 --> 00:36:47.700
Alright.

00:36:48.270 --> 00:36:49.100
Next,

00:36:49.270 --> 00:36:50.620
I'll host this meeting.

00:36:51.270 --> 00:36:54.100
Mr. Pei is willing to acquire Sky Fire
on behalf of Tengda.

00:36:54.324 --> 00:36:56.620
He'll take over everything
that belongs to Sky Fire.

00:36:57.750 --> 00:36:58.430
Of course,

00:36:58.430 --> 00:36:59.470
that includes you as well.

00:36:59.660 --> 00:37:00.540
Pei Qian.

00:37:00.768 --> 00:37:02.700
You don't need
to take such a huge detour

00:37:02.700 --> 00:37:04.350
just to humiliate me!

00:37:04.540 --> 00:37:05.430
Listen up!

00:37:05.540 --> 00:37:06.540
I quit!

00:37:06.540 --> 00:37:07.680
In your current situation,

00:37:07.680 --> 00:37:08.968
you won't find a better choice.

00:37:08.991 --> 00:37:10.100
Tengda is able to offer you

00:37:10.100 --> 00:37:11.750
the top salary in the industry.

00:37:23.910 --> 00:37:26.060
I'm a professional manager.

00:37:26.990 --> 00:37:28.310
Everything is negotiable.

00:37:29.080 --> 00:37:30.430
You're a professional indeed.

00:37:36.220 --> 00:37:37.220
What about me?

00:37:41.270 --> 00:37:42.100
Zhao,

00:37:42.700 --> 00:37:43.660
I'm thirsty.

00:37:43.660 --> 00:37:44.700
Buy me a cup of coffee.

00:37:46.820 --> 00:37:49.300
(One Month Later)

00:37:51.910 --> 00:37:53.390
Ms. Lin Wan.

00:37:53.620 --> 00:37:55.310
We renamed Sky Fire to Late Departure

00:37:55.310 --> 00:37:57.100
in hopes that you all

00:37:57.100 --> 00:37:59.124
could get used to Tengda's
slower working pace.

00:37:59.146 --> 00:37:59.990
We respected most of

00:37:59.990 --> 00:38:01.180
the staff members' wishes

00:38:01.180 --> 00:38:03.413
and allowed them to continue
working remotely from Xinyang.

00:38:03.540 --> 00:38:05.180
You all are willing to relocate

00:38:05.180 --> 00:38:07.180
to Jinchuan just to work at our HQ.

00:38:07.390 --> 00:38:08.540
It's been tough on you all.

00:38:08.540 --> 00:38:10.140
- Not at all!
- Not at all!

00:38:10.140 --> 00:38:11.830
All moving expenses

00:38:11.830 --> 00:38:13.180
will be covered by Tengda.

00:38:13.180 --> 00:38:14.650
If you have any reimbursement claims,

00:38:14.657 --> 00:38:16.280
please send them
to the Finance Department.

00:38:16.324 --> 00:38:17.540
- Okay!
- Okay!

00:38:18.350 --> 00:38:20.310
Ms. Lin Wan, we already have it easy.

00:38:20.310 --> 00:38:21.310
It's not tough at all.

00:38:21.310 --> 00:38:23.220
Tengda hired so many helpers
just to help us move.

00:38:23.220 --> 00:38:25.020
We didn't even
need to move a single thing.

00:38:25.020 --> 00:38:26.390
You also provided us
with employee dormitories.

00:38:26.390 --> 00:38:28.020
And our unit has two bedrooms
and one hall each.

00:38:28.020 --> 00:38:30.060
Yeah. It's even larger than
the unit I used to rent.

00:38:30.060 --> 00:38:31.140
You can resume your work.

00:38:31.140 --> 00:38:31.950
Get used to it first.

00:38:31.950 --> 00:38:33.310
- Okay.
- Thank you, Ms. Lin Wan.

00:38:33.310 --> 00:38:34.350
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

00:38:35.500 --> 00:38:36.140
Let's go.

00:38:36.140 --> 00:38:37.180
This is great.

00:38:37.180 --> 00:38:45.060
(Late Departure Sdudio)

00:38:54.540 --> 00:38:56.580
(Xu)

00:38:56.580 --> 00:38:57.830
(What a fulfilling day.)

00:38:57.830 --> 00:38:59.020
(Since it's still overtime,)

00:38:59.020 --> 00:39:00.790
(let's take a sip of coffee first.)

00:39:05.350 --> 00:39:07.100
(Moments, The Cyclist)
(Message delivered.)

00:39:07.100 --> 00:39:08.870
(One more message available.)

00:39:09.635 --> 00:39:10.900
(Shrimp)
(Dinner at my workplace.)

00:39:10.900 --> 00:39:12.390
(Supper will be provided after dinner.)

00:39:12.390 --> 00:39:14.350
(There's even breakfast after supper.)

00:39:23.540 --> 00:39:24.950
Once I'm done here,

00:39:24.950 --> 00:39:27.390
shift the sticker to the other side

00:39:27.390 --> 00:39:28.830
and change the filming angle.

00:39:28.830 --> 00:39:30.750
This way, no one can tell
it's the same cup.

00:39:31.140 --> 00:39:32.540
That's a brilliant idea.

00:39:32.568 --> 00:39:34.213
A cup of coffee is expensive nowadays.

00:39:34.257 --> 00:39:36.280
We can share one cup
to post on our Moments.

00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:37.580
This way, we can save some money.

00:39:37.580 --> 00:39:38.500
Yeah.

00:39:40.100 --> 00:39:41.580
Ms. Lin just liked my post.

00:39:43.180 --> 00:39:44.390
I told you already.

00:39:44.990 --> 00:39:47.140
I'm sure she didn't want us
to get off work.

00:39:47.140 --> 00:39:49.910
